body:
This PR is to fix several formatting issues in `Python API Guides`
- Add intent to below code blocks under bullet in [Graph Editor (contrib)](https://www.tensorflow.org/api_guides/python/contrib.graph_editor#Sub_graph)
    ![image](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/1680977/38141048-1ace9d42-3469-11e8-8df5-dda60b1d4d74.png)

- Fix two incorrect links in [Inputs and Readers](https://www.tensorflow.org/api_guides/python/io_ops);
   - https://www.tensorflow.org/api_guides/python/reading_data#Feeding;
   - https://www.tensorflow.org/api_guides/python/reading_data#standard_tensorflow_format

- Fix incorrect math equation rendering in [Neural Network](https://www.tensorflow.org/api_guides/python/nn#Convolution);
Before:
![image](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/1680977/38141307-0b2f2748-346a-11e8-8191-c1ae093d7694.png)
After:
![image](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/1680977/38141403-96fff234-346a-11e8-899f-d9ce8a223c5d.png)
